sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor R as Retail (Subscriber)
    participant X as REXPrimary<br/>(Sepolia)
    participant O as NavOracle<br/>(Sepolia)
    participant K as Keeper<br/>(off-chain)
    participant H as Hyperlane<br/>Bridge
    participant E as PruvExecutor<br/>(PRUV)
    participant P as Pruv RWAToken<br/>(PRUV)

    Note over R,X: PHASE 1 - Request (bất kỳ lúc nào trong epoch)
    R->>X: requestDeposit(USDC)
    X->>X: khoá USDC vào sub-queue, cấp receipt
    Note over R,X: được cancelRequest trước khi epoch chốt (ERC-7887)

    Note over X,P: PHASE 2 - Epoch initiate (Keeper trigger)
    K->>X: initiateEpoch()
    X->>O: nav()
    O-->>X: NAV (đã guard staleness)
    X->>X: matching sub-queue vs redeem-queue @ NAV
    Note over X: match P2P trước, chỉ NET delta chạm Pruv
    X->>H: bridge NET USDC sang PRUV (transferRemote)
    X->>X: đánh dấu epoch = in-flight

    Note over H,P: PHASE 3 - Thực thi ở PRUV (async)
    H-->>E: giao USDC (relay)
    E->>P: deposit(USDC, executor)
    P-->>E: wRWA shares
    E->>H: bridge wRWA về Sepolia

    Note over X,R: PHASE 4 - Settle + phân phối
    H-->>X: giao wRWA (relay)
    K->>X: settleEpoch()
    X->>X: phân phối wRWA cho subscriber theo receipt
    X->>X: epoch += 1, mở claim
    R->>X: claim(receipt)
    X-->>R: wRWA (bridged, retail tự cầm)
